    public class CoinCorr
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    Auxiliary class for GammaBetaFrame (a.k.a. GES - Gamma Efficiency Simulator). It performs basic coincidence correction for pulses.
    Author:
    Dan Fulea, 29 SEP. 2006
